Third-party model weights vendored under models/

This repository redistributes pre-trained model weights from the following
upstream projects, under their respective licenses. The weights are unmodified
and are included (via Git LFS) so the ingestion image can build and run without
downloading them.

  * Docling layout model — docling-project/docling-layout-heron
    License: Apache-2.0

  * Docling TableFormer models — docling-project/docling-models
    License: CDLA-Permissive-2.0

  * RapidOCR PP-OCRv4 OCR models (text detection / classification / recognition,
    ONNX) — from the RapidAI/RapidOCR project (PaddleOCR PP-OCRv4 weights)
    License: Apache-2.0
